comments: Roddy (MEM) contests to the side of Powell (LAC) and his hand lightly brushes Powell's back after the release of the jump shot attempt.
Westbrook (LAC) reaches in for the ball and makes contact with Biyombo's (MEM) head and arms, which affects his ability to control the ball.
Powell (LAC) establishes himself in Bane's (MEM) path and does not deliver illegal contact when setting the pick.
Biyombo (MEM) cleanly blocks Mann's (LAC) layup attempt at the basket.
Bane (MEM) jumps vertically and absorbs the contact that occurs during Mann's (LAC) layup attempt.
Harden (LAC) makes clean contact with the ball and deflects it away from Kennard (MEM) during the rebounding opportunity.
Powell (LAC) momentarily rests his hand on Kennard's (MEM) side and the contact as they move off-ball is marginal.
George (LAC) and Biyombo (MEM) engage as Biyombo moves to set the pick and marginal contact occurs as the two players disengage.
George (LAC) legally contests Bane's (MEM) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
George (LAC) firms up in Smart's (MEM) path and marginal contact occurs as they come together during the screen.
Powell (LAC) delivers contact to Biyombo (MEM) that displaces the offensive player, affecting his ability to pursue the loose ball.
Bane (MEM) loses his balance and falls on his own accord during Leonard's (LAC) drive.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) makes marginal contact with Leonard (LAC) while pursuing the rebound.
George (LAC) comes alongside Smart (MEM) and marginal contact occurs as the two players engage and disengage.
Leonard (LAC) slides his hand off of Smart (MEM) as he spins back toward the basket and the contact on the play is marginal.
Leonard (LAC) reaches in for the ball and makes contact with Smart's (MEM) left arm, which affects his SQBR during the dribble drive.
George (LAC) contests the shot attempt at the rim and avoids making contact with Roddy's (MEM) head.
Powell (LAC) firms up in Roddy's (MEM) path and does not deliver any illegal contact when setting the screen.
Roddy (MEM) legally brushes the ball during his contest of Harden's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Mann (LAC) reaches in for the ball and makes contact with Biyombo's (MEM) arms, which affects his release of the ball.

Replay review of the out of bounds called on Mann (LAC) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Biyombo (MEM) makes last contact with the ball prior to it falling out of bounds. Possession is properly awarded to Los Angeles.
Zubac (LAC) firms up over his right leg and marginal contact occurs as Smart (MEM) maneuvers around the screen.
Leonard (LAC) firms up in Bane's (MEM) path and marginal contact occurs as Bane defends around the screen.
Smart (MEM) aligns along Leonard's (LAC) path and the contact at the start of the drive is marginal.
Smart (MEM) legally contests Leonard's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
George (LAC) is retreating in Bane's (MEM) path and he absorbs the marginal contact during the drive into the frontcourt.
Bane's (MEM) left foot comes down out of bounds while he is still in contact with the ball. Possession should have been awarded to Los Angeles.
Smart (MEM) and Powell (LAC) engage and disengage during the inbounds and the contact is marginal.
Powell (LAC) reaches in for the ball and makes contact with Smart's (MEM) right arm, which affects his SQBR.

Biyombo (MEM) extends his arm out in George's (LAC) space and illegal arm contact occurs prior to George bringing two hands to the ball and beginning his upward shooting motion. A personal foul should have been assessed.
Smart (MEM) requests a timeout prior to five seconds passing after receiving the ball from the official.
Bane (MEM) releases his pass and continues toward George (LAC) when incidental foot to foot contact occurs and Bane falls to the floor.
Harden (LAC) and Roddy (MEM) engage during the inbound and marginal contact occurs as they disengage.
George (LAC) reaches in for the ball and makes illegal contact with Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) head.
Roddy (MEM) legally contests Harden's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
